name: Don't get left behind
description:
*Disclaimer*

This game escalate very quickly! Send a screenshot of your score in the comment section and let's see who's the alpha player.

Controls:

W / S - Up and Down

Goal: 

Don't get left behind by the camera and be careful of aircrafts. Houses are safe to bump but it will push you out of the camera. 

Submitted for Mini Jam 99: Birds
